{"text_id":45278,"tokens":["How"," to"," Write"," a"," Divorce"," Settlement"," Agreement","\n\n","A"," divorce"," settlement"," agreement"," is"," a"," legally"," binding"," contract"," that"," outlines"," the"," terms"," of"," the"," divorce",","," including"," property"," division",","," spousal"," support",","," and"," child"," custody","."," It"," is"," essential"," to"," craft"," a"," comprehensive"," and"," detailed"," agreement"," to"," avoid"," confusion"," and"," disputes"," in"," the"," future","."," Here","'","s"," a"," step","-","by","-","step"," guide"," on"," how"," to"," write"," a"," divorce"," settlement"," agreement",".","\n\n","**","Step"," ","1",":"," Identify"," the"," Parties","**","\n","Begin"," with"," the"," names"," of"," the"," parties","."," Write"," the"," full"," names"," of"," the"," husband"," and"," wife",","," followed"," by"," their"," addresses",".","\n\n","**","Step"," ","2",":"," State"," the"," Dates"," of"," Marriage"," and"," Separation","**","\n","Write"," down"," the"," date"," of"," marriage"," and"," the"," date"," of"," separation","."," These"," dates"," are"," crucial"," in"," determining"," the"," duration"," of"," the"," marriage"," and"," the"," marital"," assets",".","\n\n","**","Step"," ","3",":"," Express"," the"," Intention"," to"," be"," Bound","**","\n","Write"," that"," the"," husband"," and"," wife"," wish"," to"," be"," bound"," by"," the"," agreement","."," This"," statement"," indicates"," that"," both"," parties"," acknowledge"," their"," willingness"," to"," comply"," with"," the"," terms"," of"," the"," agreement",".","\n\n","**","Step"," ","4",":"," Divide"," Property","**","\n","Begin"," with"," a"," general"," statement"," on"," property"," division","."," You"," can"," choose"," to"," divide"," the"," property"," equally"," or"," according"," to"," a"," specific"," percentage","."," Write"," down"," how"," personal"," property"," is"," to"," be"," divided",","," including"," items"," such"," as"," furniture",","," vehicles",","," and"," jewelry",".","\n\n","**","Step"," ","5",":"," Divide"," Deb","ts","**","\n","Write"," down"," how"," the"," debts"," are"," to"," be"," divided","."," This"," includes"," credit"," card"," debt",","," loans",","," and"," mortgages","."," Make"," sure"," to"," specify"," who"," will"," be"," responsible"," for"," paying"," each"," debt",".","\n\n","**","Step"," ","6",":"," Address"," Minimal"," Property"," and"," Deb","ts","**","\n","If"," the"," property"," and"," debts"," are"," minimal",","," write"," a"," statement"," indicating"," that"," the"," parties"," have"," agreed"," to"," waive"," their"," claims"," to"," each"," other","'","s"," property",".","\n\n","**","Step"," ","7",":"," Determine"," Sp","ousal"," Support","**","\n","Come"," to"," an"," agreement"," on"," spousal"," support",","," also"," known"," as"," alimony","."," Write"," a"," statement"," wa","iving"," spousal"," support"," if"," applicable","."," If"," spousal"," support"," is"," required",","," write"," down"," the"," amount"," of"," support"," and"," who"," will"," be"," paying"," it",".","\n\n","**","Step"," ","8",":"," Consider"," Additional"," Terms","**","\n","Consider"," additional"," terms"," relevant"," to"," spousal"," support",","," such"," as"," the"," duration"," of"," support",","," how"," it"," will"," be"," paid",","," and"," whether"," it"," will"," increase"," or"," decrease"," over"," time",".","\n\n","**","Step"," ","9",":"," Establish"," Child"," Custody"," Arrangements","**","\n","Provide"," for"," child"," custody"," arrangements",","," including"," legal"," custody",","," physical"," custody",","," and"," visitation"," rights","."," Specify"," who"," will"," have"," primary"," custody"," and"," who"," will"," have"," secondary"," custody",".","\n\n","**","Step"," ","1","0",":"," Determine"," Visitation"," Rights","**","\n","Specify"," when",","," where",","," and"," who"," will"," pay"," for"," visitation","."," You"," may"," want"," to"," include"," a"," provision"," for"," holiday"," visitation"," or"," summer"," vacation"," schedules",".","\n\n","**","Step"," ","1","1",":"," Address"," Changes"," in"," Residence","**","\n","Include"," a"," notification"," requirement"," in"," case"," of"," a"," change"," of"," residence","."," This"," ensures"," that"," both"," parties"," are"," aware"," of"," each"," other","'","s"," whereabouts",".","\n\n","**","Step"," ","1","2",":"," Acknowledge"," Child"," Support"," Laws","**","\n","Declare"," that"," the"," couple"," is"," aware"," of"," the"," state","'","s"," child"," support"," laws","."," This"," statement"," indicates"," that"," both"," parties"," understand"," their"," obligations"," to"," support"," their"," children",".","\n\n","**","Step"," ","1","3",":"," Determine"," Child"," Support"," Amount","**","\n","S","tip","ulate"," the"," amount"," to"," be"," paid"," and"," who"," will"," be"," paying"," until"," when","."," You"," may"," want"," to"," include"," a"," provision"," for"," child"," support"," to"," be"," paid"," until"," the"," child"," reaches"," the"," age"," of"," ","1","8"," or"," completes"," college",".","\n\n","**","Step"," ","1","4",":"," Establish"," Basis"," for"," Child"," Support","**","\n","Provide"," for"," the"," basis"," of"," the"," child"," support"," determination",","," such"," as"," the"," income"," of"," both"," parties"," or"," the"," needs"," of"," the"," child",".","\n\n","**","Step"," ","1","5",":"," Divide"," Real"," Property","**","\n","Provide"," for"," division"," of"," real"," property",","," including"," the"," family"," home",","," vacation"," homes",","," or"," other"," properties","."," Specify"," how"," real"," property"," will"," be"," divided",","," including"," who"," will"," retain"," ownership"," or"," how"," it"," will"," be"," sold",".","\n\n","**","Step"," ","1","6",":"," Address"," Life"," Insurance"," and"," Tax"," Matters","**","\n","Address"," life"," insurance"," if"," applicable","."," Specify"," who"," will"," maintain"," life"," insurance"," policies"," and"," who"," will"," be"," the"," beneficiary","."," Provide"," for"," tax"," matters",","," including"," who"," will"," claim"," the"," children"," as"," dependents",".","\n\n","**","Step"," ","1","7",":"," Provide"," for"," Separation"," and"," Non","-","Inter","ference","**","\n","Provide"," for"," separation"," and"," non","-","interference","."," This"," clause"," prohibits"," both"," parties"," from"," interfering"," with"," each"," other","'","s"," lives",","," including"," contacting"," each"," other","'","s"," friends",","," family",","," or"," social"," media",".","\n\n","**","Step"," ","1","8",":"," Address"," Additional"," Instruments","**","\n","Provide"," for"," additional"," instruments",","," such"," as"," wills",","," trusts",","," or"," other"," estate"," planning"," documents","."," Specify"," who"," will"," retain"," ownership"," or"," control"," of"," these"," instruments",".","\n\n","**","Step"," ","1","9",":"," Declare"," the"," Agreement"," Entire"," and"," Binding","**","\n","Declare"," the"," agreement"," to"," be"," entire"," and"," binding","."," This"," statement"," indicates"," that"," both"," parties"," acknowledge"," that"," the"," agreement"," is"," complete"," and"," legally"," binding",".","\n\n","**","Step"," ","2","0",":"," Provide"," for"," Interpretation"," and"," Partial"," Invalid","ity","**","\n","Provide"," for"," interpretation"," of"," the"," agreement"," and"," partial"," invalid","ity","."," This"," clause"," specifies"," how"," the"," agreement"," will"," be"," interpreted"," in"," case"," of"," disputes"," or"," partial"," invalid","ity",".","\n\n","**","Step"," ","2","1",":"," Require"," Notification"," of"," Change"," of"," Address","**","\n","Provide"," for"," notification"," of"," change"," of"," address","."," This"," ensures"," that"," both"," parties"," are"," aware"," of"," each"," other","'","s"," whereabouts",".","\n\n","**","Ste